---
title: Szechuan Shrimp & Green Bean Stir-Fry with Candied Peanuts & Jasmine Rice
description: Forget takeout: The path to sweet-spicy-savory dinner bliss is as simple as breaking out a frying pan! In this recipe, ground pork and green beans are coated in a tantalizing Szechuan-style sauce, and peanuts are transformed into the perfect crunchy topping. Everything comes together over a bed of steamy rice mixed with warm, sizzly ginger—in just 30 minutes! The results? A symphony of flavors and textures that make up the perfect way to celebrate Asian History Month at your dinner table.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6501fcca7686ca60ea14b5b9-ed46b859.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6501fcca7686ca60ea14b5b9.pdf
